{"tid":1699803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰出賣Hackathon參加者個人資料","createTime":"2019-11-08T07:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T13:26:29.000Z","uid":24583,"like":340,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"b9241d10c47cf571ea5bfda8f2f8da9147371810","tid":1699803,"uid":24583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"參加左國泰Hackathon嘅你，國泰已經幫你交晒啲資料比班狗啦！<br />\n<br />\n收到消息，國泰班搞手同狗開完會，話怕會有人係比賽示威，所以會係聽日Hackathon開始入口搜袋，如果搵到你有口罩等「可疑物品」，就會將你嘅個人資料交比狗。<br />\n<br />\n個人資料就係你報名填左啲咩，雖然你冇填身分證號碼，但佢地有你<span style=\"color: red;\">全名</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">學校/公司名</span>、你出生日期個啲等等，要搵番你個人出嚟有幾難，我諗大家都心𥚃有數啦。<br />\n<br />\n講咁多都係希望參加左比賽嘅同學仔去之前三思，自己考慮下個風險，唔想你地唔知頭唔知路就比人送晒啲資料出去，更加唔想有同學仔到時比狗咬。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217ba732a24b08f607838e7ff958ceaa1868f8ec","tid":1699803,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8ecc20a5f0fb0d49de010df72f79e4ea26a21e","tid":1699803,"uid":191926,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:33:29.000Z","msg":"示威者唔好唔記得國泰城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea640ee2642c4dd714b03d8856cc8b247f452b52","tid":1699803,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6773c12e68b09fd025825fb3c6d6a8d2bc6a19","tid":1699803,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:34:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73bc4b40daec767dbace5d31e17c8dade8c38995","tid":1699803,"uid":256246,"like":76,"dislike":2,"s